# AI Incident Assistant (ServiceNow + Generative AI)

## Overview
This project integrates ServiceNow with an AI API to automatically summarize incidents and suggest resolutions.

## Features
- Incident summarization
- Resolution suggestion
- REST API integration

## Tech Stack
- ServiceNow
- JavaScript
- REST API

## Example Input
User unable to login to VPN, error authentication failed.

## Example Output
Summary: VPN login issue due to authentication error.
Suggested Fix: Reset credentials and check VPN configuration.
